    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Estimated portraits of identified or anonymous individuals based on forensic or archaeological evidence, for example, reconstructing the appearance of the person based on the skull or other remains, or by using DNA.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
